title: 2007 CAR Development Trophy
text:
The 2007 <a href="CAR%20Development%20Trophy">CAR Development Trophy</a> is the fourth edition of second level <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> tournament in Africa. The competition involves sixteen teams that are divided into two zones (North and South). Each zone is then divided into two pools of four. Each pool winner then qualifies for the final, so there is a winner for both north and south.

Final.
